# 🎬 MovieLand

Welcome to **MovieLand** – a simple and elegant movie-themed website created as part of **TASK 1 - Basics of Web Development**. This project showcases fundamental skills in **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**.

## 📌 Features

- **Hero Section**: Eye-catching landing banner with a call-to-action scroll button.
- **Trending Movies**: A responsive grid showcasing popular movies with ratings and a "Add to Watchlist" feature.
- **Star Rating System**: Interactive section where users can rate a movie using a 1–5 star system.
- **Embedded Trailers**: YouTube trailers of featured movies embedded in a responsive layout.

---

## 🛠️ Built With

- **HTML5**
- **CSS3**
- **Vanilla JavaScript**

---

## 📁 Project Structure

movieland/ │ ├── index.html         # Main HTML file ├── style.css          # Styling for the website ├── script.js          # Interactivity (watchlist & rating) └── images/            # Movie and hero section images
---

